    public abstract class FacilityActivator
extends BladeBase
implements org.osgi.framework.BundleActivator, org.osgi.service.cm.ManagedService, java.lang.AutoCloseable
    A basic activator with a Facility, with a reference to the BundleContext stored in the bundleContext property in the Facility.
